@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ofvyqp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    v0 = wp.sin((v1 * 0.86))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v2 + 0.28 + tmp + 0.39)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.39 / v2 + 0.91)) * wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.22)))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.exp(v0) / v1)
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.76 + tmp + 0.61)) * 0.12)
    v2 = ((0.39 + wp.cos(v0 + 0.03)) + v0)
    data[tid] = v0
